params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The knowledge base to import documents into. Format: projects/<Project ID>/locations/<Location ID>/knowledgeBases/<Knowledge Base ID>.

params.name: data.gcs_source
params.description: The Google Cloud Storage location for the documents. The path can include a wildcard. These URIs may have the forms gs://<bucket-name>/<object-name>. gs://<bucket-name>/<object-path>/*.<extension>.

params.name: data.document_template
params.description: Required. Document template used for importing all the documents.

params.name: data.import_gcs_custom_metadata
params.description: Whether to import custom metadata from Google Cloud Storage. Only valid when the document source is Google Cloud Storage URI.
